						               													<description>Spy Shuffle is an exciting spy themes card game where opponents battle to become the Top Spy. Played by 2-5 players from age 7+, it has a play time of 15-30 minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played by rolling a die and picking up cards according to the number that was rolled. Players starts with two cards. The first player rolls the die and picks up the number of cards that  corresponds to the number rolled on the die, If an &amp;quot;ACTION&amp;quot; card is picked up, the player  announces to the other players that they have an &amp;quot;ACTION&amp;quot; and proceed to follow the instructions listed on the Action card,  after the player performs all actions on the card, then it becomes the next player's turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is won by collecting 5 special spy cards, but there are bumps and blockages along the way via Action cards that dictate your actions and what cards you keep or let go of. Wild cards are also in the mix that causes you to exchange half your hand with another player and Snitch cards that you can use to affect your opponents win&amp;hellip;&amp;hellip;.becoming Top Spy is the aim but only if you can play your cards right.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
